22
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:13,660
They are supposed to fight to win victory for Zhen Hua.

23
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:15,340
You, as the commanders,

24
00:01:16,020 --> 00:01:17,289
should be on the alert.

25
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,100
Lin Yang of your class

26
00:01:20,100 --> 00:01:21,010
sit on the top 5.

27
00:01:21,010 --> 00:01:22,810
Good job. Hang in there.

28
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:24,810
If anything goes wrong, you will bear the blame.

29
00:01:26,610 --> 00:01:28,250
As for Ling Xiangqian and Yu Zhouzhou,

30
00:01:29,610 --> 00:01:31,240
raise their scores by 20 points.

31
00:01:32,210 --> 00:01:33,810
Let's surpass the Affiliated High School.

32
00:01:34,250 --> 00:01:34,930
Got it?

33
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:38,140
One more thing.

34
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:41,660
Should we hold the basketball game?

35
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,060
I think it is worth discussing.

36
00:01:46,979 --> 00:01:48,170
Well, Director Pan,

37
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:49,810
I think

38
00:01:49,810 --> 00:01:53,370
the kids are worn out by studying every day,

39
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:55,740
so they take this game very seriously.

40
00:01:56,170 --> 00:01:57,140
That's true, Director Pan.

41
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,570
Frankly speaking, the kids are having rough days.

42
00:02:00,250 --> 00:02:01,660
How could we

43
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:03,420
cancel their extracurricular activities?

44
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:04,810
Even the NBA would cancel games,

45
00:02:05,370 --> 00:02:07,490
is our basketball game more important than the NBA?

46
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:09,940
Um...

47
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:12,450
I have to say something.

48
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:13,520
Mr. Zhang,

49
00:02:14,090 --> 00:02:15,580
no offense,

50
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:18,420
but Director Pan made a point this time.

51
00:02:20,980 --> 00:02:22,940
Indeed we should pay attention to

52
00:02:22,940 --> 00:02:24,500
the students' grades.

53
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,890
Director Pan has been teaching for many years

54
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:28,579
and has rich experience.

55
00:02:28,579 --> 00:02:30,940
I think we class teachers

56
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:35,010
should fully implement Director Pan's ideas.

57
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,610
We should focus on the grades,

58
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,720
and also cherish the opportunity of the basketball game.

59
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:42,890
Tell the students to play it well after we go back.

60
00:02:48,890 --> 00:02:49,500
Mr. Wu,

61
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:50,340
sit down.

62
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:52,810
Why?

63
00:02:53,490 --> 00:02:54,890
What do you mean?

64
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:55,980
Didn't I say to cancel it?

65
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:57,420
Why did you make it go ahead?

66
00:02:58,730 --> 00:03:00,300
Didn't you say to discuss it?

67
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:04,300
How could it be "worth discussing" if we cancel it?

68
00:03:04,650 --> 00:03:07,220
That would be "no discussion", right?

69
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,340
No...

70
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:09,980
Pan,

71
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:12,220
you've been a leader for years,

72
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:13,500
but your ability of expression

73
00:03:14,090 --> 00:03:15,220
has declined.

74
00:03:16,450 --> 00:03:17,730
I'm going to give a class.

75
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:30,070
[Episode 7 Take Off Points Of Your Class]

76
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:33,940
Morning, Mi Qiao!

77
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:34,880
Morning!

78
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,090
Zhouzhou,

79
00:03:41,650 --> 00:03:42,610
which one is more handsome?

80
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,250
This one.

81
00:03:49,450 --> 00:03:50,610
I still think this one is better.

82
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:51,980
