88
00:03:57,370 --> 00:03:59,300
Wu Wenlu won't care.

89
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:02,170
I didn't know you liked basketball.

90
00:04:02,170 --> 00:04:03,580
Let me tell you. I just got addicted to it.

91
00:04:04,650 --> 00:04:05,580
Although he's not very tall,

92
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,340
only 183cm,

93
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:09,890
he is a real man on the basketball court!

94
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:11,370
Isn't 183cm tall?

95
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:13,060
Not in the NBA.

96
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:16,140
In our school, 183cm is OK.

97
00:04:16,329 --> 00:04:17,089
Hey,

98
00:04:17,490 --> 00:04:20,700
come with me to watch the boys play basketball after class today.

99
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,810
Lin Yang who always sticks to you

100
00:04:22,810 --> 00:04:24,460
seems to play well.

101
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:25,580
Oh.

102
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,370
I have some homework to do.

103
00:04:28,490 --> 00:04:29,490
What a bummer!

104
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:39,580
What's the smell?

105
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:40,490
It smells like...

106
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:41,490
baked bun slices.

107
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:44,420
Benben gave them to me at the gate. You want some?

108
00:04:44,900 --> 00:04:46,740
Of course I'll eat it.

109
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,580
Wow!

110
00:04:50,250 --> 00:04:51,650
I do like this.

111
00:04:51,650 --> 00:04:52,090
So nice!

112
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:52,860
Oh,

113
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:55,360
here it is.

114
00:04:56,050 --> 00:04:56,860
Perfect!

115
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:00,620
Let me get this straight.

116
00:05:01,330 --> 00:05:02,490
There's so much information.

117
00:05:03,650 --> 00:05:04,810
That's to say,

118
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:06,900
the tragedy happened to Yu Zhouzhou's family

119
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,090
because of a ticket?

120
00:05:12,140 --> 00:05:14,250
That's why Yu Zhouzhou has been ignoring you for a year,

121
00:05:14,250 --> 00:05:15,460
and you haven't been very proactive?

122
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:20,370
Yesterday was Zhouzhou's mom's death day,

123
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:22,450
so finally she was willing to talk about it?

124
00:05:26,410 --> 00:05:27,580
Here is my question.

125
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:28,210
Go ahead.

126
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,770
When Yu Zhouzhou was crying,

127
00:05:33,010 --> 00:05:35,050
did you hold her in your arms?

128
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:36,620
Get lost!

129
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:37,810
Seriously,

130
00:05:37,930 --> 00:05:38,409
let me tell you something.

131
00:05:38,409 --> 00:05:40,580
Girls are at their most vulnerable time when crying.

132
00:05:41,050 --> 00:05:41,860
If it were my Qianqian,

133
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:43,300
I would hug her immediately.

134
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,240
The atmosphere would be so good.

135
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,620
How dare I?

136
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:49,330
Finally she's willing to open up.

137
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:50,930
How dare I push it?

138
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:53,210
That's right.

139
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:55,420
Yu Zhouzhou has suffered such a big blow.

140
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:58,450
No wonder I felt something was wrong this year.

141
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:00,530
I just think of it...

142
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:02,650
Such a big thing happened and you didn't tell me anything.

143
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:03,930
Do you still regard me as your friend?

144
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:04,740
Ouch!

145
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:06,140
You're overacting.

146
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,860
How about now? What are you going to do?

147
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:10,810
I've no idea.

148
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:13,900
I just hope that before I leave I can hear her say

149
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,050
she will not blame me anymore.

150
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,930
In this way she can completely let go the pain,

151
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,040
and I can start over again without feeling guilty.

152
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:20,650
I think...

153
00:06:21,370 --> 00:06:22,890
no one should be blamed for this.

154
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:27,460
Before you leave? Where are you going?

155
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,700
I'm transferring to another school.

156
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:30,740
Transfer schools?

157
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,020
To the Affiliated High School.

158
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:33,210
My dad's working on it.

159
00:06:33,210 --> 00:06:34,450
The arrangements will be done next week.

160
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:36,900
What's wrong with you?

161
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,330
It's such a big thing but you didn't tell me.

162
00:06:38,330 --> 00:06:39,700
What kind of a friend are you?

163
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:41,050
I was afraid you would cry and beg me not to leave.

164
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:41,930
What if I weaken?

165
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:44,180
Then don't go. Why are you transferring schools!

166
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:45,370
For over one year

167
00:06:45,370 --> 00:06:46,620
everything that I've done for Yu Zhouzhou

168
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,650
was to find out

169
00:06:47,650 --> 00:06:48,930
whether she still blames me or not.

170
00:06:48,930 --> 00:06:49,970
Now I know

171
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,700
I can never hear her say that,

172
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:53,700
but I'm no longer asking for it.

173
00:06:54,530 --> 00:06:56,180
Maybe only my departure

174
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,330
could free Yu Zhouzhou from her pain.

175
00:06:58,890 --> 00:06:59,900
Lin Yang, I just want to know...

176
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,900
Leaving is the last thing that I can do for her.

177
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:04,210
Fine.

178
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:10,420
Good shot!

179
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:12,760
Why are you here?

180
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,460
Do you know that the basketball game will be held next week?

181
00:07:14,770 --> 00:07:16,300
If your class is up against us,

182
00:07:16,490 --> 00:07:17,490
be prepared to be defeated.

183
00:07:17,490 --> 00:07:18,740
I might not even participate.

184
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,570
Why not?

185
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:23,980
I'm transferring to the Affiliated High School.

186
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:25,930
Why? What happened?

187
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:29,090
Nothing. It's just easier to get a recommendation
in the Affiliated High School.

188
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:31,920
Come on. Isn't it because of Yu...

189
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:35,580
Yu...What?

190
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:36,420
Yu Huai.

191
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:40,290
Yu Huai? You don't have to worry about him.

192
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:42,490
Iâ€˜m kind of vacating a place in the race for everyone.

193
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:43,920
In this case,

194
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,460
we have all the more reason to have a friendly game.

195
00:07:45,810 --> 00:07:47,370
When will you leave?

196
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:49,770
Next week. The arrangements are almost done.

197
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:51,740
That's a deal. You must come.

198
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:53,580
It's really boring without you.

199
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,140
You should think about it carefully.

200
00:07:55,140 --> 00:07:56,090
If I participate,

201
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:57,740
there would be no chance for your class.

202
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:01,640
I just like the way you brag

203
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:03,050
with a straight face.

204
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:04,620
Be prepared to be defeated!

205
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:13,580
Why can we bump into you everywhere?

206
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:16,020
Mi Qiao, Zhouzhou, what a coincidence!

207
00:08:16,730 --> 00:08:19,020
Since we've met, let's sit and eat together.

208
00:08:27,370 --> 00:08:28,140
Oh,

209
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:30,050
this is Xin Rui, a new student in our class.

210
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:31,180
Hello!

211
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:36,130
Zhouzhou, I have to tell you something.

212
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:42,330
Xin Rui, there are lots of...

213
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,330
mysterious snacks in Zhen Hua's cafeteria.

214
00:08:43,330 --> 00:08:45,010
Let's get more dishes.

215
00:08:45,450 --> 00:08:46,420
I have enough food.

216
00:08:48,330 --> 00:08:49,320
Let's go.

217
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:00,940
What did you want to tell me?

218
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,420
Nothing. It's nothing.

219
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,770
Let's eat. I'll talk to you after lunch.

220
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:35,090
Why are they having lunch together?

221
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:37,450
It's none of your business.

222
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,130
Keep your eyes on your own tray.

223
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,090
It's the braised pork you took!

224
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:46,820
I just ate your shredded meat.

225
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,010
I won't eat it. You can take it.

226
00:09:51,010 --> 00:09:52,450
Xin Rui, you don't have to be polite with her. You eat.

227
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,300
Zhouzhou,

228
00:09:57,890 --> 00:09:58,650
I...

229
00:09:58,650 --> 00:09:59,500
Lin Yang,

230
00:10:00,570 --> 00:10:02,300
I'm looking for you everywhere. Zhouzhou's here, too.

231
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:04,890
The game schedule is set.

232
00:10:04,890 --> 00:10:06,860
Friday afternoon. We happen to have 2 self-study periods.

233
00:10:07,130 --> 00:10:07,940
No problem.

234
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:12,380
You hid it quite well.

235
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:20,940
Come to watch my basketball game.

236
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:22,380
Why?

237
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:26,690
Because I play basketball pretty well.

238
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,380
I'll see at the time.

239
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:31,420
Okay.

240
00:10:32,890 --> 00:10:34,180
Actually this week I...

241
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:36,060
What is it?

242
00:10:36,650 --> 00:10:37,570
Nothing.

243
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,010
Nothing.

244
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:05,650
Hey, did he just confess his love to you?

245
00:11:05,650 --> 00:11:07,450
Nonsense.

246
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:09,940
What's going on?

247
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:10,890
This?

248
00:11:10,890 --> 00:11:13,060
This is the benefit that the Animation Club got for us.

249
00:11:13,300 --> 00:11:14,200
How's it?

250
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,060
The students who don't go home at noon can watch animations,

251
00:11:16,060 --> 00:11:17,090
and relax.

252
00:11:17,330 --> 00:11:20,210
We need to thank our Class Monitor Ling for her support.

253
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,260
It doesn't feel right. I almost got distracted by you.

254
00:11:26,010 --> 00:11:26,860
I think...

255
00:11:27,570 --> 00:11:29,010
Lin Yang is a good guy.

256
00:11:29,010 --> 00:11:30,570
What do you think about him?

257
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:32,330
Stop talking, or I'll draw on your poster.

258
00:11:32,810 --> 00:11:33,770
Don't touch my man!

259
00:11:33,770 --> 00:11:34,500
My bad! No!

260
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:37,760
Ling Xiangqian.

261
00:11:52,210 --> 00:11:54,530
My classmates are like that. I hope you don't mind.

262
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:55,180
It's nothing.

263
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:56,770
As long as you don't mind, I'm OK with it.

264
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,330
I've finished the book. Thank you!

265
00:11:59,100 --> 00:12:00,030
[Decisive Moments in History]

266
00:12:02,770 --> 00:12:04,650
