267
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:06,090
Mi Qiao brought it.

268
00:12:06,090 --> 00:12:07,450
It's Hayao Miyazaki's Castle in the Sky.

269
00:12:07,450 --> 00:12:09,530
Aren't cartoons only for kids to watch?

270
00:12:09,530 --> 00:12:10,500
You like them?

271
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,940
I haven't watch cartoons for a long time.

272
00:12:11,940 --> 00:12:13,090
But it's fun.

273
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,970
Isn't that because you are still a kid?

274
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,260
Maybe.

275
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:18,300
I gotta go.

276
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:23,060
I'm sorry!

277
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,380
Sorry!

278
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:26,980
Taking these to the office?

279
00:12:27,090 --> 00:12:27,640
Yeah.

280
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:29,060
Let me help you.

