00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:29,770
No, thanks.

282
00:12:29,770 --> 00:12:30,690
It's OK. Let me do it.

283
00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:31,930
OK, thanks.

284
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:33,420
See you.

285
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:34,820
OK.

286
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:36,330
Did I hurt you?

287
00:12:36,330 --> 00:12:37,180
No.

288
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:54,770
Lin...

289
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:55,570
Lin...What?

290
00:12:55,570 --> 00:12:56,260
Benben.

291
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:57,500
Come on. Let's take some BBQ skewers.

292
00:12:57,770 --> 00:12:58,650
I don't want to eat.

293
00:12:59,420 --> 00:13:00,570
Then let's go to an internet cafe?

294
00:13:00,570 --> 00:13:01,880
I don't know how to play computer games.

295
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,690
How about playing billiards?

296
00:13:04,690 --> 00:13:05,330
Name a place.

297
00:13:05,330 --> 00:13:06,170
I'll come with you.

298
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:08,860
Let's go!

299
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:09,450
Let's go!

300
00:13:21,450 --> 00:13:23,090
If you feel bored, you are free to leave.

301
00:13:23,090 --> 00:13:23,890
It's not boring.

302
00:13:23,890 --> 00:13:25,000
Be quiet.

303
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:26,210
It's very interesting.

304
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,050
Have you told Yu Zhouzhou?

305
00:13:31,690 --> 00:13:32,500
Not yet.

306
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:34,380
I kept it all day but didn't know how to tell her.

307
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:37,300
I bet she's the only one in our school who doesn't know.

308
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,060
It doesn't matter whether she knows.

309
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:40,940
I'll never hear her say that.

310
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:44,130
That won't work. There should be a kiss goodbye!

311
00:13:44,130 --> 00:13:44,620
Get lost!

312
00:13:47,890 --> 00:13:49,530
You're a typical case of being angry when embarrassed!

313
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:09,770
Hello.

314
00:14:10,180 --> 00:14:12,060
Mi Qiao, I'm in a bookstore.

315
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:13,000
Call you later.

316
00:14:13,690 --> 00:14:14,500
Don't hang up.

317
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:15,970
Yu Zhouzhou,

318
00:14:15,970 --> 00:14:17,860
do you know Lin Yang's transferring schools?

319
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:21,300
Where did you hear the rumor?

320
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:22,980
I just bumped into Zhan Yanfei at the stationery,

321
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:24,090
She was buying a gift for Lin Yang.

322
00:14:24,090 --> 00:14:25,500
She said Lin Yang would leave next week.

323
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:27,530
No way.

324
00:14:27,530 --> 00:14:29,180
Why not?

325
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:31,860
I have to hang up. Let's talk tomorrow.

326
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:42,740
Take it slowly.

327
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:44,010
I'm fine.

328
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:45,530
Why did you drink so much?

329
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:47,680
Couldn't you just drink a little less?

330
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:48,770
Yang.

331
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,380
Yang!

332
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:51,060
Coming!

333
00:14:51,530 --> 00:14:53,260
Get your dad some water.

334
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:54,570
He's drunk.

335
00:14:54,570 --> 00:14:55,260
OK.

336
00:14:58,250 --> 00:14:59,860
Director Hao said so.

337
00:15:00,890 --> 00:15:02,820
There are 3 honors classes in the Affiliated High School

338
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:06,860
and all the head teachers are provincial top-notch teachers.

339
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:09,940
Yang can choose any class he wants when he goes there.

340
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:13,440
How can I not express some gratitude?

341
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,210
You can't say that without drinking, can you?

342
00:15:16,690 --> 00:15:17,530
You don't know that.

343
00:15:17,530 --> 00:15:18,300
Dad.

344
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:27,010
Yang,

345
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,500
Director Hao asked me to bring you

346
00:15:31,130 --> 00:15:33,330
to the Affiliated High School tomorrow to look around,

347
00:15:33,890 --> 00:15:35,860
to get familiar with the school first.

348
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,740
OKay.

349
00:16:50,530 --> 00:16:51,940
On the day of the performance,

350
00:16:52,090 --> 00:16:54,420
the boss asked Benben if he was ready.

351
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:59,020
[Youth&Children Story Contest]

352
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:57,060
Benben said, "I have one more request."

353
00:16:57,330 --> 00:16:59,010
The boss asked, "What request?"

354
00:16:59,180 --> 00:16:59,980
Benben said,

355
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:02,420
"Please buy me a big yellow balloon,

356
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:05,900
and release it when I'm giving the performance.

357
00:17:06,290 --> 00:17:07,280
No matter how far,

358
00:17:07,329 --> 00:17:09,619
my friend could see it,

359
00:17:09,810 --> 00:17:13,050
and she will know that I've realized my dream."

360
00:17:13,690 --> 00:17:14,810
Thank you!

361
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:30,020
I went to check at the gate but there were only red ones.

362
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,260
Thank you.

363
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:54,660
Benben,

364
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:56,540
why are you here?

365
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,930
Zhouzhou, take me in for one night.

366
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:00,450
Come on in.

367
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,170
Be careful.

368
00:18:04,050 --> 00:18:05,290
Slow down.

369
00:18:17,930 --> 00:18:18,660
Thanks.

370
00:18:18,660 --> 00:18:19,540
No worries.

371
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:26,500
Zhouzhou,

372
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,980
you're so nice.

373
00:18:39,450 --> 00:18:40,900
Are your dad drunk again?

374
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:41,900
Yeah.

375
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:45,090
When I was a kid, he drank a few times in a week.

376
00:18:46,020 --> 00:18:48,660
Now he get sober a few times in a week.

377
00:18:49,090 --> 00:18:51,410
Why don't you go find your biological father?

378
00:18:52,690 --> 00:18:54,020
Why should I?

379
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,610
Except for not beating me,

380
00:18:56,210 --> 00:18:57,380
he's not much better.

381
00:18:59,090 --> 00:19:00,680
Now there's one good thing.

382
00:19:01,010 --> 00:19:02,660
I don't have to count the bruises for my lifetime.

383
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,050
The lifetime will be over like that.

384
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:10,290
Zhouzhou,

385
00:19:10,690 --> 00:19:12,050
it's my turn to protect you.

386
00:19:12,930 --> 00:19:14,330
I won't let anyone bully you.

387
00:19:17,810 --> 00:19:18,400
Zhouzhou,

388
00:19:19,210 --> 00:19:20,610
are you asleep?

389
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:23,450
Benben,

390
00:19:25,170 --> 00:19:27,020
Lin Yang said he was leaving.

391
00:19:28,690 --> 00:19:29,500
Transfer schools?

392
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:32,050
How did you know?

393
00:19:32,690 --> 00:19:33,980
I went to find him once,

394
00:19:34,290 --> 00:19:35,740
to warn him to stay away from you.

395
00:19:37,170 --> 00:19:38,260
So it is true.

396
00:19:38,330 --> 00:19:39,090
Sure.

397
00:19:40,090 --> 00:19:42,620
A guy like him should get far away,

398
00:19:43,170 --> 00:19:44,450
the further the better.

399
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:47,090
I'm pissed off that he always shows up in front of you.

400
00:19:47,450 --> 00:19:48,620
How could he forget what he did to you?

401
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:49,500
Benben...

402
00:19:54,090 --> 00:19:55,090
Zhouzhou.

403
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:02,210
That accident had nothing to do with him.

404
00:20:02,770 --> 00:20:04,020
I did it for your own good.

405
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:06,500
Why do you all know what is for my good?

406
00:20:06,500 --> 00:20:08,170
Why only do I not know it?

407
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,330
Zhouzhou...

408
00:20:19,690 --> 00:20:21,780
I'm fine. Go to sleep.

409
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:36,540
It seems that all the people around me

410
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:39,540
never get the chance to say goodbye

411
00:20:41,050 --> 00:20:42,810
before they never see me anymore.

412
00:21:00,290 --> 00:21:02,260
Hey, is Lin Yang here today?

413
00:21:03,170 --> 00:21:04,290
No.

414
00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:05,780
His seat is still empty.

415
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:06,690
Thanks.

416
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:13,290
The classroom is a place for studying.

417
00:21:13,690 --> 00:21:15,290
It's very improper to stick the posters on your desk!

418
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:16,780
Tear it off right now!

419
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:19,020
I like him, so when I have it on my desk,

420
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:19,930
I'd like to study.

421
00:21:20,050 --> 00:21:22,660
It's none of your business!

422
00:21:23,140 --> 00:21:24,210
How dare you!

423
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,020
You tore my man!

424
00:21:31,810 --> 00:21:33,690
You tore my man!

425
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:35,980
Pan Yuansheng, I'll kill you!

426
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:37,660
Pan Yuansheng!

427
00:21:37,860 --> 00:21:38,660
Pan Yuansheng!

428
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:41,020
I'll kill you!

429
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:42,020
Pan Yuansheng!

430
00:21:42,020 --> 00:21:44,780
I'm telling you. This isn't over.

431
00:21:47,330 --> 00:21:48,380
I'm talking to you.

432
00:21:50,890 --> 00:21:53,530
I like him, so when I have it on my desk,

433
00:21:53,530 --> 00:21:54,410
it makes me feel like studying.

434
00:21:54,410 --> 00:21:55,450
Stay out of it.

435
00:21:55,450 --> 00:21:56,260
What did you say?

436
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:57,930
You are out of my control, right?

437
00:21:57,930 --> 00:21:59,540
Get Mr. Wu to come to my office.

438
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:02,860
No, Director Pan. My bad. I was wrong.

439
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:05,900
You're right.

440
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:07,730
I'll tear it off right now.

441
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:22,370
Director Pan.

442
00:22:22,370 --> 00:22:23,050
I was looking for you.

443
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:24,330
Tell me about Lin Yang.

444
00:22:24,930 --> 00:22:26,890
I was just about to report it to you.

445
00:22:26,890 --> 00:22:27,860
Let's go.

446
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:33,860
I'm not afraid of you.

447
00:22:34,210 --> 00:22:35,900
I have my own reason.

448
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:38,450
You are the one who violated my rights first.

449
00:22:40,930 --> 00:22:42,500
Then don't tear it up if you're so capable.

450
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,330
Stop laughing at me.

451
00:22:44,330 --> 00:22:46,040
You helped me stick it, so help me tear it off.

452
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:47,980
Come on, help me tear off the tapes.

453
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:50,620
Mi Qiao,

454
00:22:52,090 --> 00:22:53,740
give up so easily?

455
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:55,900
I have another one.

456
00:22:57,020 --> 00:22:57,780
By the way,

457
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:59,740
are you going to watch

458
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,620
the basketball game between Class 1 and Class 2?

459
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:03,440
It's Lin Yang's farewell game.

460
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,780
He was so devoted to you.

461
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:07,450
This would be his last game.

462
00:23:07,450 --> 00:23:09,090
If you don't even show your face,

463
00:23:09,090 --> 00:23:10,690
it would be too...

464
00:23:12,740 --> 00:23:13,540
What?

465
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,170
Nothing.

466
00:23:30,330 --> 00:23:30,810
Jiang Chuan!

467
00:23:30,810 --> 00:23:31,570
Oh!

468
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:33,860
You scared the heck out of me.

469
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,330
Did Lin Yang come to school today?

470
00:23:37,210 --> 00:23:37,900
No.

471
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:40,570
He went to the Affiliated High School.

472
00:23:41,260 --> 00:23:42,020
He left today?

473
00:23:43,210 --> 00:23:44,570
No, just to look around today.

474
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:45,930
He will transfer next week.

475
00:23:47,090 --> 00:23:47,780
You knew it?

476
00:23:48,860 --> 00:23:50,090
Do you know why he's leaving?

477
00:23:50,690 --> 00:23:51,410
Don't you know?

478
00:23:52,260 --> 00:23:53,290
Haven't you forgiven him?

479
00:23:54,980 --> 00:23:55,900
Forgive him?

480
00:23:57,090 --> 00:23:58,570
Forget it.

481
00:24:04,050 --> 00:24:05,450
Excuse me, I gotta go.

482
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:17,900
Qianqian,

483
00:24:18,690 --> 00:24:19,380
what are you doing here?

484
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:21,930
When did you know that Lin Yang was leaving?

485
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:25,380
Just yesterday.

486
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:29,090
How could he do this?

487
00:24:29,690 --> 00:24:30,570
Yeah,

488
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:32,140
it's so ridiculous.

489
00:24:32,140 --> 00:24:32,730
Jiang Chuan!

490
00:24:33,740 --> 00:24:35,740
What does Lin Yang have to do with me?

491
00:24:35,740 --> 00:24:37,290
You knew it but you didn't tell me either.

492
00:24:37,290 --> 00:24:38,450
I found out when I came to school this morning.

493
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,740
I must be the last one in our grade

494
00:24:40,740 --> 00:24:41,810
to know that he's transferring.

495
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,080
Not you.

496
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:44,330
Yu Zhouzhou is the last one.

497
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:46,740
Yu Zhouzhou?

498
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:48,380
I just met her.

499
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:52,980
How can Zhouzhou compare with me?

500
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,570
Before kindergarten,

501
00:24:56,570 --> 00:24:57,380
three of us have been together.

502
00:24:59,090 --> 00:25:02,140
I thought we would go to college together,

503
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:03,140
and work together,

504
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:05,980
and live in the same neighborhood,

505
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,050
so we can often hang out together.

506
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:09,900
What did he do?

507
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:11,980
Just walked away and left us.

508
00:25:12,450 --> 00:25:13,810
Does he regard me as his friend?

509
00:25:21,450 --> 00:25:21,980
That's right.

510
00:25:29,140 --> 00:25:30,380
It would be better if it could rain a little bit.

511
00:25:30,740 --> 00:25:31,450
What?

512
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:33,500
What did you say?

513
00:25:35,410 --> 00:25:36,620
Everything will be fine.

514
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:41,690
Zhouzhou.

515
00:25:43,620 --> 00:25:44,540
Why are you here?

516
00:25:45,260 --> 00:25:46,260
I have something to tell you.

517
00:25:47,980 --> 00:25:48,930
Say it.

518
00:25:50,170 --> 00:25:50,930
Actually...

519
00:25:53,290 --> 00:25:54,500
I'm transferring to another school.

520
00:25:55,850 --> 00:25:56,450
I knew.

521
00:25:57,500 --> 00:25:59,140
You knew?

522
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:01,130
Almost the whole school knows,

523
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,410
how could I not know?

524
00:26:03,930 --> 00:26:05,260
I didn't hide it from you on purpose.

525
00:26:05,690 --> 00:26:07,140
I wasn't blaming you.

526
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:08,860
I'm sorry!

527
00:26:09,540 --> 00:26:11,740
Lin Yang, can you stop saying that?

528
00:26:12,290 --> 00:26:13,500
I don't blame you anymore.

529
00:26:14,330 --> 00:26:15,450
If you transfer schools

530
00:26:15,450 --> 00:26:16,440
or even drop out,

531
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,050
it's to get my forgiveness.

532
00:26:18,500 --> 00:26:19,260
Fine.

533
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:21,140
I can tell you right now,

534
00:26:21,410 --> 00:26:22,290
that I've already forgiven you.

535
00:26:22,490 --> 00:26:24,170
You don't have to keep doing this to remind me.

536
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:26,130
Zhouzhou, I didn't mean that.

537
00:26:26,450 --> 00:26:28,260
It's not your fault.

538
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:29,900
I'm only blaming myself.

539
00:26:30,450 --> 00:26:31,740
If what I said then

540
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:32,780
hurt you,

541
00:26:35,260 --> 00:26:36,210
I apologize.

542
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:37,410
Zhouzhou, don't go.

543
00:26:37,740 --> 00:26:38,380
Zhouzhou!

544
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:40,660
Listen to me! Listen to me!

545
00:26:41,260 --> 00:26:42,530
Stop being so childish!

546
00:26:56,210 --> 00:26:57,050
I can't do it.

547
00:26:57,540 --> 00:26:58,540
I can't do it anymore.

548
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:03,290
It's just a farewell game. You don't have to...

549
00:27:08,540 --> 00:27:11,410
How is the Affiliated High School? Isn't it good?

550
00:27:12,210 --> 00:27:14,130
Did they get you cheerleaders?

551
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:16,540
Anyone prettier than my Qianqian?

552
00:27:17,290 --> 00:27:18,200
Well, you don't...

553
00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:19,850
don't have to answer it.

554
00:27:20,260 --> 00:27:21,980
If you say yes, I won't believe that.

555
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:30,330
Aren't you not leaving?

556
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,090
Why?

557
00:27:32,450 --> 00:27:34,980
Since there's the news you're leaving,

558
00:27:34,980 --> 00:27:36,620
the relationship between Qianqian and I

559
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,450
has flowered by leaps and bounds.

560
00:27:41,170 --> 00:27:42,050
You don't have to worry about it.

561
00:27:50,290 --> 00:27:51,140
Why?

562
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:55,570
Didn't Yu Zhouzhou ask you to stay?

563
00:28:00,570 --> 00:28:01,410
Jiang Chuan,

564
00:28:06,380 --> 00:28:07,740
Zhouzhou and I are over.

565
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:39,000
[Whoever tears it is a dog]

